Name: assign_worker_to_team
Description: Whether a worker is assigned to a team

Name: select_feature_for_sprint
Description: Whether a feature is pulled into the sprint

Name: schedule_user_story_to_sprint
Description: Sprint number a user story is scheduled to

Name: allocate_budget_to_feature
Description: Allocated budget to a feature in currency

Name: assign_scrum_master_to_team
Description: Whether a Scrum Master supports a team

Name: commit_sprint_goal
Description: Whether the sprint goal is committed

Name: include_user_story_in_sprint_backlog
Description: Whether a user story is in the sprint backlog

Name: mark_blocker_for_resolution
Description: Whether a blocker is selected for resolution

Name: choose_release_plan_for_feature
Description: Whether a feature is part of the release plan

Name: assign_product_owner_to_backlog
Description: Whether a Product Owner manages a backlog
